Task
Is the name suitable for a child?
The parents decided to name the child with a 5-letter name, and that it must begin with the letter A. Would name be suitable for this family as a child's name?
Create a variable name and assign it the value of an arbitrary string (name). 
Create an isCorrect variable and assign it a boolean expression that evaluates to true 
if the first letter of the name is A and the length of the name is 5, and false otherwise.

Solution
const name = 'Alice';
const isCorrect = name[0] === 'A' && name.length === 5;
